程序包 com.iafenvoy.annotationlib.annotation.registration

Annotation Interface Link

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(FIELD) public @interface Link

Tell the registry system to link this object to a registered object.

Field with this annotation must be non-final, or registration system will throw an error.

Field with this annotation should be null, or value will be overwritten.

For example, if you have registered a block, you can create an item field with this annotation. Registration system will create a BlockItem and give it to the field.
